These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, car, van, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
2. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Transport   | van | car | scooter | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
City: hannover, london, venice, paris
1. the person traveling to hannover is not to the right of the person traveling to paris##8
2. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to venice##2
3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| City   | hannover | venice | london | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, ambient, metal, r&b
1. the fan of metal is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of ambient is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | r&b | ambient | metal |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, bridge, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing billiard##7
2. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8
3. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Game   | billiard | snooker | bridge | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
